{"tid":274332,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"823 周年業績發佈會 (節錄）","createTime":"2017-06-07T08:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T11:43:58.000Z","uid":34621,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"721c683e34555605aa6b9ed83d8f81168ffa42b2","tid":274332,"uid":34621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:47:31.000Z","msg":"由於全程英文 小弟英文唔太好 敬請原諒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基金經理A :<br />\n彌敦道700 號就黎開 有冇d 新嘅資訊可以比我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGeorge:<br />\n冇啊屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基金經理B: <br />\n黎緊會唔會繼續賣資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果會賣 有冇話賣邊d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGeorge:<br />\n唔肯定 但係賣邊d 會詳細研究。 不過我地上年賣資產平均有14定40% premium 請放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基金經理C:<br />\n買撚咗咁多大陸野之後 集團未來重心會放喺大陸定香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGeorge<br />\n一定係香港 因為香港我地團隊最多人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基金經理D :<br />\n點解買廣州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGeorge<br />\n因為之前歐美滙 嘅成功 令我地想複製<br />\n有人之前擔心人仔貶值會 仆街。<br />\n不過冇事啦依家 屌撚哂你班垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下題目由webcast 提問（ 老散）<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">咁啱兩條都係我嘅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n題目 1 ：<br />\n集團早前講過 中國資產上限係12.5% ， 未來有冇機會提高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGeorge :<br />\n唔撚會啊屌你 除非揾到個project 好撚正 如果唔係都唔柒會多過12.5%<br />\n<br />\n題目2<br />\n恒基早前 以天價購入美利道停車場發展office , 集團會否考慮喺cbd 買多d 資產or 起多d office<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGeorge:<br />\n唔撚會再起office 啊撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你班老散知唔撚知 平時d 商鋪揾多咗錢 我地有得分鳩佢d profit 但係office d 公司冇撚得分 因為佢地唔撚會踩鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過點都要有d office 做diversification <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上海 同埋九龍灣就係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於發展方面 我地冇能力喺對面海買office 因為冇撚錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n短評<br />\nGeorge 今次答問題幾有誠意<br />\n<br />\n股東大會又唔見佢咁有誠意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次股東大會就趕住走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次就問到冇問題先走<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過冇得揀  strong hold<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7846ef9184ce8491cc581a52b670a70d023719","tid":274332,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:50:47.000Z","msg":"好有現場感<br />\n<br />\n仿佛有聲<br />\n<br />\n多謝報導<br />\n<br />\n預測：仍有上升空間<br />\n<br />\n利申：手上沒有持有823"},{"pid":"e22d8680d5dc7d63cdbdc0daa79a7e59bc07c48e","tid":274332,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300e7e356453b4e48b16c473aea1099b9de8580b","tid":274332,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201